column2: select m.PLATEIFU, m.RA, m.DEC, w.w1mpro as w1, w.w2mpro as w2, w.w3mpro as w3, w.w4mpro as w4, SQRT (POWER (( (w.ra-m.RA) *cos ((m.DEC) * (#/#) )) , #) + (POWER ((w.dec-m.DEC) , #) )) *# as AngSep into temp_manga from mydb.MaNGA_drp_mpl7 m, WISE_allsky w where w.ra between (m.RA-#) and (m.RA+#) and w.dec between (m.DEC-#) and (m.DEC+#)
